{
  "name": "[APEX] 06 - Matter Opening Orchestrator",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## [APEX] 06 - Matter Opening Orchestrator\n\n**Purpose:** Full matter opening automation. On approval, runs LEAP conflict check, creates matter, generates and sends costs agreement via PandaDoc (template selected by matter type), creates Google Drive folder structure, logs key dates to calendar, triggers InfoTrack property search for conveyancing, notifies fee earner, creates standard tasks in LEAP, and logs to Airtable.\n\n**Trigger:** POST to /webhook/new-matter-approved\n\n**Payload:** `{ clientId, clientName, clientEmail, matterType (Conveyancing/Family Law/Litigation/Commercial), feeEarnerId, supervisingPartnerId, propertyAddress, estimatedFee, billingType, keyDates[] }`\n\n**Credentials to swap before activating:**\n- `LEAP_API_KEY` → LEAP Bearer token (used in HTTP header)\n- `PANDADOC_API_KEY` → PandaDoc API key\n- `GOOGLE_DRIVE_CRED_ID` → Google Drive OAuth2\n- `GOOGLE_CALENDAR_CRED_ID` → Google Calendar OAuth2\n- `INFOTRACK_API_KEY` → InfoTrack API key\n- `SLACK_CRED_ID` → Slack OAuth2\n- `AIRTABLE_CRED_ID` → Airtable Personal Access Token\n\n**Placeholders to replace:**\n- `{{LEAP_API_BASE}}` → LEAP API base URL\n- `{{PANDADOC_CONVEYANCING_TEMPLATE}}` → PandaDoc template UUID\n- `{{PANDADOC_FAMILY_LAW_TEMPLATE}}`, `{{PANDADOC_LITIGATION_TEMPLATE}}`, `{{PANDADOC_COMMERCIAL_TEMPLATE}}`\n- `{{MATTERS_PARENT_FOLDER_ID}}` → Google Drive parent folder ID\n- `{{FIRM_CALENDAR_ID}}` → Google Calendar ID\n- `{{AIRTABLE_BASE_ID}}` → Airtable base ID\n\n⚠️ Google Calendar node creates the FIRST key date only. Wrap in SplitInBatches loop for multiple dates.",
        "height": 460,
        "width": 800,
        "color": 6
      },
